     1	//! `OrtBgeEmbedder` — cross-vendor ONNX-Runtime BGE-small embedder.
     2	//!
     3	//! A caller-supplied `impl fathomdb_embedder_api::Embedder`, sibling of
     4	//! `candle_bge` / `nomic`, that produces `BAAI/bge-small-en-v1.5` vectors
